The 7th Hammer fight is supposed to be done in his chamber.  All the other "judges" encircling the room cast the AE's, which are part of the event.  Pulling 7th hammer to the entrance, thereby bypassing the AE's to which the mob had been tuned, and bypassing the requirement that everyone had completed the trials, was an exploit, no matter how you look at it.
