				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The only difference between the monk epic 7th Hammer and the normal pop spawn 7th Hammer is the drops.  The mob, ae's, hitpoints, dps, etc, are all the same.  
<br />

<br />
I guess consider yourself lucky you didn't get any AE's during your monk fights.  Something must have been bugged that day on your server.  It's not like that has never happened before.
<br />

<br />
The monk epic 7th Hammer fight still has AE's, and everything else is the same, with the exception of the loot on the corpse when he dies.  The monk epic version only has the monk epic piece.  The PoP version has normal 7th Hammer loot.
