				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The 4 back to back 7th hammer hits we did for our monks all had AE's.  The devs have said this fight was the same as the normal fight, except for the loot.  The other guilds that have done this that I've talked also all had AE's.
<br />

<br />
What possible reason would they have to change the encounter for an epic hit?
<br />

<br />
At lvl 70 with maxed resists, I resisted a large portion of the AE's.  Perhaps yall just resisted them too, and thought there weren't any /shrug.
